Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.71,0:00:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall we begin deceleration thruster control?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.98,0:00:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't checking for hazards\Non the docking course come first?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.49,0:00:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Does it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.91,0:00:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll check the operations sheet.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.89,0:00:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.70,0:00:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Can we really make it to Plant Quetta?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.00,0:00:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the perfect distance\Nfor a practice flight.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.09,0:00:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! Now what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.58,0:00:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Aliya, there's an emergency\Ncall from Room 11.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.05,0:00:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Tiko and the others...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.46,0:00:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'll go check on them!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.73,0:00:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? But...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.67,0:00:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You can rely on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.00,0:00:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.08,0:00:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Suletta sure is wound up.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.60,0:00:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,She's probably excited to see Aerial again.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.42,0:00:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You think that's it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.85,0:00:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotta work hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.13,0:00:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotta work hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.28,0:00:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotta work hard... Gotta work hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.86,0:00:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Otherwise, I'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.18,0:00:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm really counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.40,0:00:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, I want you to lead\Nour next project, Nika.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.16,0:00:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Not Ms. Belmeria?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.38,0:01:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll ask her for support.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.90,0:01:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,But I want you to surpass her.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.98,0:01:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for overestimating me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.12,0:01:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Unbelievable...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.04,0:01:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I... had to hide.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.43,0:02:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sensor post 098.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.16,0:02:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Detailed observation to airspace area 08.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.04,0:02:57.08,Default - On top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Respond to administrative bureau...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.08,0:02:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A nearby ship...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.08,0:02:59.61,Default - On top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...for pre-docking inspection.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.67,0:03:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}…has reported an unidentified object.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.61,0:03:03.34,Default - On top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Halt your ship in the specified area.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.53,0:03:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It may be a tool dropped...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.34,0:03:05.62,Default - On top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wait for an inspector to board.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.35,0:03:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...by a worker outside the plant.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.62,0:03:07.62,Default - On top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}At the customs clearance platform...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.15,0:03:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A recovery team is on standby.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.62,0:03:09.53,Default - On top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}…submit in the designated format...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.48,0:03:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If necessary...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.53,0:03:11.18,Default - On top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...names of hazardous cargo...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.18,0:03:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,We're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.31,0:03:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We somehow managed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.41,0:03:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe we should have more confidence?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.06,0:03:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,We practiced ship navigation in class, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.63,0:03:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Could someone take this cargo for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.61,0:03:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.14,0:03:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you. I owe you one.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.61,0:03:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do my best!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.16,0:03:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.14,0:03:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotta work hard. Gotta work hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.40,0:03:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotta work hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.77,0:03:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.20,0:03:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.86,0:03:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.29,0:03:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Just look at this app.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.96,0:03:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's beyond useless!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.74,0:03:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't complain.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.96,0:03:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,We went for price over performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.88,0:03:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Suletta!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.22,0:03:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.07,0:03:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems Quiet Zero is coming along well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.70,0:04:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You brought a Gundam here\Njust so you could confirm that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.50,0:04:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you, Lady Prospera?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.40,0:04:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Call me Elnora Samaya...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.59,0:04:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,if you prefer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.43,0:04:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,In that last duel with Grassley,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.11,0:04:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Aerial's permet score reached six.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.92,0:04:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,GUND-ARM, Inc. has also\Nserved as good camouflage--
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.45,0:04:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Show me your right hand\Nthis instant, Lady Prospera.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.83,0:04:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though it's been more than 20 years,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.92,0:04:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,are you still afraid of witches?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.55,0:04:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Rajan...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.69,0:04:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,This reflects Aerial's\Nnetwork architecture pattern.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.84,0:04:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,With this data, Quiet Zero\Ncan proceed to its final stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.45,0:04:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, it's still my project.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.75,0:04:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,But of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.01,0:04:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Olcott.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.02,0:05:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Transfer of additional\Narmament will be finished soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.07,0:05:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Install Beltablads\Nfor me, Bessie, and Gristan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.02,0:05:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Norea!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.63,0:05:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Sophie?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.29,0:05:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.34,0:05:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,She's with Naji.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.36,0:05:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,We won't take any lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.82,0:05:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,We simply want to discuss\Nthe disparities between Earth and space.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.41,0:05:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's discuss, shall we?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.19,0:05:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you guys piloting Desultors?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.05,0:05:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Bob?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.02,0:05:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Those are Jeturk mobile suits.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.54,0:05:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,They may be outdated,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.78,0:05:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,but they're not something\Nterrorists like you could easily obtain.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.78,0:05:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Bob, cut it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.30,0:05:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the real thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.94,0:05:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You were watching me just now, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.82,0:05:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me give you a closer look.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.74,0:05:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it, Sophie.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.67,0:05:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.65,0:05:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.93,0:05:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't do anything crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.65,0:06:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want the ship, you can have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.01,0:06:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,But let my employees go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.45,0:06:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.81,0:06:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be needing your cooperation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.17,0:06:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Settings complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.66,0:06:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing much.\NJust go about your work as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.36,0:06:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,While keeping quiet about us…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.72,0:06:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Do your work as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.44,0:06:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.99,0:06:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Lunch is ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.40,0:06:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.29,0:06:25.08,Default - On top,,0,0,0,,Boy, I'm hungry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.08,0:06:28.73,Default - On top,,0,0,0,,I bought a lot. Take what you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.80,0:06:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,For me...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.73,0:06:30.11,Default - On top,,0,0,0,,Sounds good!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.10,0:06:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Chicken over...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.54,0:06:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What'll it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.74,0:06:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.96,0:06:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,G-Go ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.38,0:06:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine. You were first, Suletta.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.09,0:06:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.09,0:06:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.91,0:06:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.11,0:06:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,If you say so... thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.62,0:06:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Suletta!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.90,0:06:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you choose?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.56,0:06:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going to eat all that yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.11,0:06:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot. I'm taking these to the bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.15,0:06:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,For Miorine and Nika.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.76,0:06:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,For Ms. Miorine?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.45,0:06:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Want to come with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.03,0:07:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, uh... no, I'm fine here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.66,0:07:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Suit yourself. Well, I'm off.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.86,0:07:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.39,0:07:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,There's none... left...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.95,0:07:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, don't talk with your mouth full!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.17,0:07:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you care?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.23,0:07:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You're talking too, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.58,0:07:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Nuno!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.75,0:07:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I brought one for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.01,0:07:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.68,0:07:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I have one already.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.68,0:07:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.78,0:07:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess this is lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.75,0:07:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no one's fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.25,0:07:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I must have miscounted.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.59,0:07:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, we'll use\NHatch 3 to load Aerial.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.27,0:07:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take a video. Let Suletta know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.10,0:07:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you tell her yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.67,0:07:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.71,0:07:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened between you and Suletta?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.11,0:07:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't say it like I did wrong
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.77,0:08:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Not everyone can be like you, Miorine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.49,0:08:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.03,0:08:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,The request Sarius made to press\Ncharges for GUND Format use...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.69,0:08:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I hear it was rejected.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.04,0:08:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Was that on your orders, Mr. President?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.89,0:08:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It was Cathedra's decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.24,0:08:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,That may be the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.14,0:08:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,However, Sarius won't give up that easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.16,0:08:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Eventually, he'll try to crush\Nyour daughter's company.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.52,0:08:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Grassley should be sanctioned\Nfor stirring unrest.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.83,0:08:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,And of course, I'll gladly cooperate.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.66,0:08:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,For the future of the Benerit Group.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.44,0:08:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm told your eldest son, Guel Jeturk,\Nhas yet to be found.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.53,0:08:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Rather than my daughter,\Nperhaps you should worry about your own--
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.21,0:08:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,There it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.42,0:08:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the reason I've never liked you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.59,0:08:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Some ex-soldier butting in\Nfrom outside and claiming everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.23,0:08:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Jeturk!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.86,0:09:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,If it was stolen from you,\Nyou were merely too weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.75,0:09:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'll steal it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.18,0:09:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,And when that happens,\Nyou'd better not complain!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.23,0:09:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Please take your leave for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.98,0:09:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So he won't take the bait...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.02,0:09:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I planted a transmitter on Delling's guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.21,0:09:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm now leaving Plant Quetta.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.76,0:09:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Begin the operation in two hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.89,0:09:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. Two hours from now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.92,0:09:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It must be tough being adopted.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.52,0:09:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Do your best to win Daddy's love.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.83,0:09:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That old man has some nerve. What a jerk.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.78,0:09:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,He gives me the creeps.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.36,0:09:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Sabina!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.57,0:09:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Send the signal to the Dawn of Fold.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.74,0:09:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell them to begin immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.48,0:09:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.36,0:09:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.08,0:09:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What about the two hours?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.57,0:09:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,We've received the go-ahead code\Nthrough the secure line.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.06,0:09:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The Prince has given us the green light.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.28,0:09:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.79,0:10:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll wait in the cockpit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.70,0:10:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Sophie?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.27,0:10:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Sophie?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.38,0:10:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Norea!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.47,0:10:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,This girl is amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.09,0:10:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Look. She fought six-on-one!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.04,0:10:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,How long are you\Ngoing to watch these videos?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.71,0:10:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.77,0:10:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Gundam!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.98,0:10:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It can fly! It can dance!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.22,0:10:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Aerial!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.36,0:10:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Suletta Mercury...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.62,0:10:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd love to meet her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.67,0:10:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if I ever will.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.88,0:10:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The Captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.24,0:10:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true! They say he was an ace pilot.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.06,0:10:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,He couldn't even fit\Nin the seat with that belly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.28,0:10:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I was thinner back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.73,0:10:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain KenanjI!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.33,0:10:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Dominicus was created to correct injustice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.75,0:10:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,That includes talking behind\Npeople's backs.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.49,0:10:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,W-We're sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.49,0:10:47.75,Default - On top,,0,0,0,,W-We're sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.70,0:10:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.83,0:10:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Captain...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.87,0:10:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We've detected a fleet ID code\Non a standard course to the Moon.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.84,0:10:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's a Jeturk ship.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.27,0:11:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Its name is Wormblood.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.67,0:11:04.99,Default,,0,0,0,,From the plant patrol fleet?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.99,0:11:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would it be there?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.02,0:11:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Suletta?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.06,0:11:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Now that you mention it...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.01,0:11:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,With Aerial, maybe?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.52,0:11:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that makes sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.54,0:11:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Unbelievable...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.66,0:11:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did she disappear to now?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.45,0:11:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.70,0:11:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You're here too, Bel?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.40,0:11:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I came to retrieve Aerial.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.87,0:11:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I was informed of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.38,0:11:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,How nice that GUND medical treatment\Nmay finally become a reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.14,0:11:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's thanks to Suletta and her friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.01,0:11:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,My daughter does me proud.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.64,0:11:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.31,0:11:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,We've arrived at the plant.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.79,0:11:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I heard. Bel was just here.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.02,0:11:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I see...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.47,0:11:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Suletta, is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.52,0:11:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Huh?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.36,0:11:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't call me\Njust because you're here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.32,0:12:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.49,0:12:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm kind of scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.96,0:12:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Of what?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.08,0:12:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Of everyone.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.39,0:12:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my, I thought you said\Nyou were making friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.92,0:12:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That was a misunderstanding.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.67,0:12:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was just carried away.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.80,0:12:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, no one trusts me with anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.06,0:12:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,They don't need me at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.52,0:12:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is that what they told you?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.60,0:12:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Not exactly...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.86,0:12:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,But… when I started to think\Nthat's how they see me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.04,0:12:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything I thought was fun...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.80,0:12:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The things I enjoyed...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.74,0:12:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,They all turned against me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.41,0:12:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And now...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.85,0:12:45.99,Default,,0,0,0,,they're scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.50,0:12:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Suletta...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.02,0:12:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Are you crying?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.84,0:12:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's weird, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.71,0:12:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't mean to...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.59,0:12:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're caught up in your worries.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.18,0:13:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}C Block, Hangar 78.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.61,0:13:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.77,0:13:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Your mother and Aerial\Nare waiting for you there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.18,0:13:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Come say hello.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.23,0:13:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! I'm coming! Right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.94,0:13:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, I'll call you again when I get there!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.63,0:13:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I-I'm on my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.91,0:13:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.89,0:13:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing, sulking in here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.37,0:13:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,S-S-sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.77,0:13:31.92,Default - On top,,0,0,0,,Just tell me if you have a problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.83,0:13:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Miorine!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.46,0:13:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't on purpose!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.09,0:13:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Get back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.84,0:13:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Quit running away!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.42,0:13:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,B-But...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.54,0:13:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,If you have something to say,\Nthen say it to my face!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.18,0:13:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.93,0:13:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing I want to say!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.60,0:13:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Liar!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.32,0:14:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! Stay put, already!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.90,0:14:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.76,0:14:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,and your… freakish stamina!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.07,0:14:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Miorine?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.49,0:14:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.82,0:14:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotcha!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.02,0:14:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-That's a dirty trick!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.98,0:14:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's called cunning, stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.46,0:14:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it because I'm stupid…\Nthat you won't rely on me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.36,0:14:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.21,0:14:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.44,0:14:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm useless,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.39,0:14:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,a weed to be eaten,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.38,0:14:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,and you use me as a shield.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.54,0:14:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,When I couldn't eat\Na chicken over rice lunch,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.02,0:14:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't have the courage to say\Nthere were no lunches left.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.71,0:14:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.27,0:14:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,If this is how it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.59,0:14:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I never should have come to the school.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.86,0:14:46.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you putting yourself down?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.97,0:14:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to your motto?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.18,0:14:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Move forward, gain two, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.19,0:14:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.73,0:14:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Why the heck not?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.25,0:14:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't do it all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.17,0:15:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Moving forward is always... scary...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.76,0:15:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I say it... to push myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.21,0:15:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone like you, Ms. Miorine...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.56,0:15:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,would never get that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.18,0:15:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Never--
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.26,0:15:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You are so stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.56,0:15:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You called me stupid again!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.44,0:15:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me you know what I was like!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.63,0:15:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I was sick of all of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.88,0:15:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,The duels and my lousy father!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.40,0:15:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I wanted to run!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.26,0:15:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to go to Earth!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.65,0:15:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.85,0:15:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because you became my groom!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.20,0:15:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You and your stupid\N"move forward, gain two!"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.04,0:15:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I have to run a company,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.62,0:15:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,listen to my father's infuriating criticism,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.96,0:15:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and bow my head!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.40,0:15:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.49,0:15:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the one who doesn't get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.88,0:15:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you see I'm happy like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.43,0:15:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because of you that I don't\Nhave to run away anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.93,0:15:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.94,0:16:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't run from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.65,0:16:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,If you have something to say, say it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.74,0:16:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Annoy me like always and move forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.70,0:16:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Miorine...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.02,0:16:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Say you want me to rely on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.16,0:16:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that... okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.94,0:16:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.90,0:16:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Say it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.64,0:16:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.46,0:16:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.21,0:16:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Please... rely on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.59,0:16:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay at my side forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.24,0:16:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. I'll stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.12,0:16:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,And don't lose any duels.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.66,0:16:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't lose. Ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.16,0:16:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And give the tomatoes more compost!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.93,0:16:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.75,0:16:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Use the Andes model for the sunlight pattern.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.66,0:16:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Clean my room twice a week!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.77,0:16:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,And email me three times a day!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.20,0:16:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Miorine, are you crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.91,0:16:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't look!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.94,0:16:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.93,0:16:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't believe what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.49,0:17:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.00,0:17:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Because...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.96,0:17:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm your groom.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.22,0:17:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Plant Quetta to shipping vessel Kashtanka.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.49,0:17:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Your ship is now entering\Nplant security airspace.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.14,0:17:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Please maintain docking course.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.52,0:17:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Kashtanka. Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.25,0:17:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Awaiting pre-docking security inspection.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.42,0:17:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Olcott!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.92,0:17:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We're within range\Nfor the comms jamming pods.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.77,0:17:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The time lag for the cloaking\Nprogram is five seconds.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.17,0:17:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It should be fine\Nfrom this distance, right?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.98,0:17:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger, Bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.27,0:17:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Olcott, Desultor, send me out!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.67,0:17:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Bridge, we're now beginning the operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.67,0:17:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Bessie, Gristan, let's move.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.04,0:17:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Copy that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.04,0:17:49.57,Default - On top,,0,0,0,,Copy that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.26,0:17:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Mobile suits detected within\Nthe front's restricted airspace.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.16,0:17:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,There are three of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.67,0:18:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Permet ID codes?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.04,0:18:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,No corresponding codes found.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.51,0:18:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,They're unregistered machines.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.69,0:18:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Contact the front management company.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.23,0:18:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is Front Control.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.55,0:18:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Attention, mobile suit pilots.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.88,0:18:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You are not authorized to use\Nmobile suits in restricted airspace.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.16,0:18:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Repeat.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.91,0:18:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You are not authorized to use\Nmobile suits in restricted--{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.87,0:18:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Comms jamming pods deployed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.40,0:18:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,To the outside, it'll look\Nlike a signal failure.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.29,0:18:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Switch to hopping transmission.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.67,0:18:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Sophie! Norea!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.17,0:18:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,On it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.97,0:18:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Sophie Pulone, Lfrith Ur...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.80,0:18:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Norea Du Noc, Lfrith Thorn.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.67,0:18:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Beginning operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.94,0:18:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Lame.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.06,0:18:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Don't you think it's cute?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.10,0:18:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.73,0:18:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,But, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.28,0:19:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It just looks like a gift from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.54,0:19:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.55,0:19:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.10,0:19:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Miorine is inside Plant Quetta.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.93,0:19:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Our only target is Delling.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.64,0:19:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,If luck is with her, she'll survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.64,0:19:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Emergency warning B-1 issued.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.04,0:19:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Emergency warning B-1 issued.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.93,0:19:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't get a signal.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.61,0:19:31.39,Default - On top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Please evacuate...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.39,0:19:35.32,Default - On top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...to the indicated shelter.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.28,0:19:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.64,0:19:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,We may be under attack by hostile forces.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.08,0:19:37.32,Default - On top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Repeat...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.32,0:19:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,"Hostile?"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.32,0:19:40.90,Default - On top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Emergency warning B-1 issued.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.36,0:19:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Who the hell would attack here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.85,0:19:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,How am I supposed to know?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.24,0:19:44.37,Default - On top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Emergency warning B-1 issued.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.06,0:19:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,They could be terrorists.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.05,0:19:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Please hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.35,0:19:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You must take shelter.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.87,0:19:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,We should evacuate, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.78,0:19:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.61,0:19:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Prepare Aerial for activation.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.01,0:19:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.93,0:20:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't leave you behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.64,0:20:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Norea! Before we deployed the pods,\Nwe detected the target signal in C Block.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.47,0:20:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.82,0:20:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.45,0:20:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Time for some carving!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.77,0:20:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Sophie?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.41,0:20:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Follow my timing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.77,0:20:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You follow mine! I'm going first!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.27,0:20:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That damned adoptee double-crossed me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.82,0:20:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,How was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.45,0:21:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Bridge.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.30,0:21:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}C Block has been disconnected.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.28,0:21:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Confirmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.68,0:21:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Norea, you rendevous with Olcott's team.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.66,0:21:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll disable all the ports.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.10,0:21:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Copy that!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.97,0:21:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Sophie, you provide a diversion as planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.78,0:21:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No way!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.37,0:21:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sophie!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.65,0:21:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We just have to kill that Delling guy, right?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.03,0:21:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So let me take the lead!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.72,0:21:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That fool...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.65,0:21:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Miorine!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.57,0:21:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Suletta...?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.49,0:21:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Miorine? Ms. Miorine!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.33,0:21:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What do I do? What do I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.86,0:21:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,A mobile suit?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.34,0:22:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.87,0:22:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What in the world? What the heck is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.72,0:22:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Suletta Mercury?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.41,0:22:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I get to meet you already!\NHow cool is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.02,0:22:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you, Ms. Witch from Mercury.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.06,0:22:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Sophie Pulone,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.90,0:22:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,a witch from Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.86,0:23:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Next time on {\i0}\NMobile Suit Gundam: The Witch from Mercury,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.75,0:24:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Keep Marching on Instead of Running Off."{\i0}
